Nadine de Rothschild https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nadine_de_Rothschild 0 Nadine de Rothschild (née Nadine Lhopitalier; born 18 April 1932) is a French author and former actress. She is the widow of banker Edmond Adolphe de Rothschild, a member of the Rothschild family.
